  "title": "Petrol Station Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>We are a Retailer managing Caltex Petrol Stations in Singapore for the past 20 years.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Lead the daily operations of a Caltex Petrol Station around Serangoon / Hougang, driving customer satisfaction and operational excellence through effective team management and retail experience.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage station operations to ensure efficient service delivery and high customer satisfaction</li><li>Lead and motivate the team to achieve sales targets and maintain operational standards</li><li>Implement customer-oriented strategies to enhance the customer experience at the petrol station</li><li>Monitor inventory levels and coordinate timely replenishment to avoid stockouts</li><li>Ensure compliance with safety and regulatory requirements at the petrol station</li><li>Resolve operational issues promptly to maintain smooth station functioning</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years of retail experience to effectively manage customer interactions and sales operations</li><li>Educational qualification of A Level, Diploma, or higher to support operational and administrative tasks</li></ul>",
